&gt;&gt;male #12: [inaudible] why are there traditions
about what you eat or whatever in monasteries

00:43:29.441 --> 00:43:32.270
if they are staying away from modern world?

00:43:32.270 --> 00:43:38.099
&gt;&gt;Rinpoche: -stricter in monasteries? -away
for outer world? -why the mon-better? In general

00:43:38.099 --> 00:43:44.150
there's many mentalities and many different
ways, because you can meditate everywhere,

00:43:44.150 --> 00:43:54.349
any time, but we are busy and lazy. It's like
meditation wise you can, but personal wise

00:43:54.349 --> 00:44:06.160
you cannot. Because too busy and lazy. So
if you go to the special retreat and you can

00:44:06.160 --> 00:44:14.220
put more effort to the meditate and spend
all time, something like that. Yes.

00:44:14.220 --> 00:44:28.830
&gt;&gt;male #13: Some people believe that like
for chronic injuries that there's a mental

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.400
[inaudible] mental there's like a part of
