&gt;&gt;Rinpoche: Yeah, I think many people now
are using meditation as too to recover mental

00:44:45.980 --> 00:44:46.980
disease.

00:44:46.980 --> 00:44:55.260
&gt;&gt;male #13: No, no, no, like physical problem
like some people have back pain for a lot

00:44:55.260 --> 00:44:56.819
of years [inaudible].

