Rinpoche: Physical problem, right...oh...mmm
mmm. That's not just like magic. You can meditate

00:45:01.869 --> 00:45:11.810
now and tomorrow, boom- finish, no. But never-the-less
it helps. For example, I'm guinea pig and

00:45:11.810 --> 00:45:18.250
scientist put me inside machine and the put
inject- kind of like chemical and it produce-

00:45:18.250 --> 00:45:30.190
what you call this, blister, blister and then
meditate. And say how you heal the blisters

00:45:30.190 --> 00:45:40.900
and this is a dramatic result. The meditator
heal the bli-blister much faster than people

00:45:40.900 --> 00:45:47.259
who control diet and physical exercise, the
control group. There's some kind of like-

00:45:47.259 --> 00:45:53.069
when you meditate change in you're the cells
and develop immune systems that really helps.

00:45:53.069 --> 00:46:02.690
But also depends on what kind of problems.
Actually it's good for the mental for the

00:46:02.690 --> 00:46:13.559
mind. It's good. Can take on any problem as
support for meditation. For example, I used

00:46:13.559 --> 00:46:25.880
to be by panic and, but that's what we call
natural suffering. Getting old, see, die,

00:46:25.880 --> 00:46:33.579
these are natural suffering. So this is not
easy to transform, but self-created suffering

00:46:33.579 --> 00:46:41.500
can transform. The worst suffering for us,
death and fear of death. Which one is more

00:46:41.500 --> 00:46:49.009
painful? Fear of death. The fear of death
is self-created suffering. Death is natural

00:46:49.009 --> 00:46:57.410
suffering. That's why most suffering for us
is self-created suffering, and that can liberate

00:46:57.410 --> 00:47:01.609
by meditation. Thank you.
